item.title: Need help compiling
item.dc:creator: @Extoz Extoz
item.description:
@Extoz wrote:

Open up notepad and paste this:

@echo off Title Compiler "C:\Program\Java\jdk1.6.0_06\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause

Then save it as compiler.bat and run it.

Edit this to your verison of JDK and where it’s placed.

"C:\Program\Java\jdk1.6.0_06\bin\javac.exe" *.java
